; Coverage test for report.cc fn_set_commodity_price
; Test set_commodity_price() which programmatically sets a price for a
; commodity. The function takes (amount, datetime, price) and returns
; NULL_VALUE. We then use market() to verify the price was set.

2024/01/01 Buy
    Assets:Stock    10 AAPL
    Assets:Cash    $-1000.00

test reg Assets:Stock --format '%(set_commodity_price(amount, [2024/06/01], $150.00))%(market(amount, [2024/06/01]))\n'
$1500.00
end test
